<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>كِتَابُ الزَّكَاةِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> تَجِبُ فِي خَمْسَةِ أَشْيَاءَ:</span> بَهِيمَةِ أَنْعَامٍ، وَنَقْدٍ، وَعَرْضِ تِجَارَةٍ، وَخَارِجٍ مِنَ الأَرْضِ، وَثِمَارٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span class="c5"> بِشَرْطِ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> إِسْلَامٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَحُرِّيَّةٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَمِلْكِ نِصَابٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> وَاسْتِقْرَارِهِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[٥]</span> وَسَلَامَةٍ مِنْ دَيْنٍ يَنْقُصُ النِّصَابَ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[٦]</span> وَمُضِيِّ حَوْلٍ،<span class="c5"> إِلَّا فِي:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- مُعَشَّرٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَنِتَاجِ سَائِمَةٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- وَرِبْحِ تِجَارَةٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- وَإِنْ نَقَصَ فِي بَعْضِ <span class="c2">(١)</span> الحَوْلِ بِبَيْعٍ أَوْ غَيْرِهِ - لَا فِرَاراً -: انْقَطَعَ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) قوله: (بعض) سقطت من (أ).</p> </div>